comments: Garland (CLE) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Rose (DET).
Thompson (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Maker (DET) and absorbs the contact.
Thompson (CLE) makes incidental contact with Brown (DET) as he goes for the loose ball.
Garland (CLE) makes marginal contact to the body of Rose (DET) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Thompson (CLE) wraps Drummond (DET) in the post.
Sexton (CLE) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Brown (DET) and cleanly blocks the shot.
Drummond (DET) makes contact to the arm of Thompson (CLE) that affects his release of the shot attempt.
Garland (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Maker (DET) with his arms extended, but the contact is marginal.
Maker (DET) maintains a legal guarding position during the shot attempt in the post by Love (CLE).
Thompson (CLE) could be deemed to be in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Drummond (DET) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Sexton (CLE).
Thompson (CLE) makes marginal contact to the body of Drummond (DET) during the drive.
Thompson (CLE) grasp the arm of Drummond (DET) as he gathers and enters his shooting motion.
Love (CLE) briefly grasps Maker's (DET) jersey, but does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Thompson (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Maker (DET) and does not deliver contact.
McKinnie (CLE) maintains a legal guarding position on Rose (DET) during the drive and cleanly dislodges the ball.
Galloway (DET) commits a take foul on Sexton (CLE).
